Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:15.18,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感情的代名词
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:19.19,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不胜枚举
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:22.80,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若你的眼神在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:26.86,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我便靠本能来判断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:27.45,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trust　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:28.71,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}纠葛难分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:29.36,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trash　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:34.10,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}光明与黑暗 相随相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:38.04,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仿若珍珠 连成一串
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:42.05,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自有缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:46.50,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶然也好 自然也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:51.22,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终将化作期待的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:54.94,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.79,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始渐渐上升
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:23:01.80,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有伪装 亦无需试探
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:06.36,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做最真的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:10.34,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坚守信仰 不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:13.95,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:15.79,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:17.79,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:20.64,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my further future
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.64,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.70,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すべてが今
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:02.05,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my further future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.49,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:04.92,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:07.08,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君のそばで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:09.66,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be my further future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:15.18,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感情の名前なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:19.19,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言い出せばキリがないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:22.80,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君の目が叫ぶのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:26.86,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本能で聞き分ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:27.45,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trust
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:28.71,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}付き纏う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:29.36,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trash
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:34.10,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そこにある 光も闇も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:38.04,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}つながりだす ビーズのように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:42.05,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}理由があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:46.50,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶然でも 成り行きでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:51.22,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信じたい出会いに変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:54.94,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心の温度が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.79,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少しずつ上がるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:23:01.80,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見せかけじゃない 駆け引きもない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:06.36,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当の自分のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:10.34,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}選んだ場所に立ってること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:13.95,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君に伝えたいよ
